        <Document ID="D8A050A6-EBA8-4E9C-9883-86270BC2BECE">
            <Text>Thelma (?) or Ramona (?)
Age • Location

Role in Story
An ode to my Aunt Thelma. Basically just tell her story, with a good bit of flourish around the edges.

Goal


Physical Description


