            <Title>Bestiary</Title>
            <Text>Hopefully some of this can be generated by software. 

Don’t want to simply repeat / copy items found in Gamma World, though some “odes” would be appropriate. 
Don’t want to over-do, especially in the Saskan Lands. Leave more exotic stuff for the Lewshanana, the Form, the Krbsh Sea, Krbshanana and the Komexicon.

